rComments: Elisabetta is one of those teachers who wants to cultivate the best kind of learning environment for her students. Her background in philology is excellent and complementary to her teaching . She is engaged, charismatic, passionate and very professional, always prepared with fantastic slides. Truly one of U of Ts finest language instructors
Shes the best instructor I ever met at University of Toronto!!!! She really cares students and be excellent at teaching. The BEST instructor!!!!!

Elisabetta is my favourite professor in Italian Department. She is so responsible and she works hard on making the lecture more fun and we never get bored. We learn so much knowledge from the lectures. She is a wonderful and amazing professor, that is the reason why I take her class ITA320 again after ITA100.

Absolutely fantastic, has so much enthusiasm towards teaching and student-teacher interaction. Was always available outside of class for help or clarification. She really made the class inclusive and positive where everyone wanted to partake in. I would take every class she teaches!
